    "content": {
        "rendered": "\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"13044\" class=\"elementor elementor-13044\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b08e0c2 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"b08e0c2\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-77b10ee e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"77b10ee\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fe35927 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"fe35927\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h1 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">THE BRAND<\/h1>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ac7ae20 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ac7ae20\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-acb15ac e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"acb15ac\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-98e3bb3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"98e3bb3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">WELCOME TO 50 Shades <\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dad56fd elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"dad56fd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Searching for the best Black hair stylist near you? If so, you have arrived at the premier destination in Everett. Since being established in 2013, 50 Shades  Salon has evolved into a private, high-end hair sanctuary. The brainchild of Blessing Chitanda, 50 Shades  is dedicated to treating the hair of women of all ethnicities with a specialized focus on African American hair care and luxury extensions.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-61be2c7 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"61be2c7\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a8414c9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"a8414c9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https:\/\//\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/blessing-chitanda-owner-studio-27-black-hair-stylist-everett.webp\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-15004\" alt=\"Portrait of Blessing Chitanda, owner of 50 Shades  Salon and premier Black hair stylist in Everett, MA.\" srcset=\"https:\/\//\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/blessing-chitanda-owner-studio-27-black-hair-stylist-everett.webp 800w, https:\/\//\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/blessing-chitanda-owner-studio-27-black-hair-stylist-everett-200x300.webp 200w, https:\/\//\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/blessing-chitanda-owner-studio-27-black-hair-stylist-everett-683x1024.webp 683w, https:\/\//\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/blessing-chitanda-owner-studio-27-black-hair-stylist-everett-768x1152.webp 768w, https:\/\//\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/blessing-chitanda-owner-studio-27-black-hair-stylist-everett-600x900.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-52047db e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"52047db\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-860a51f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"860a51f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-24ff1de elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"24ff1de\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https:\/\//\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/luxury-natural-hair-care-texture-studio-27-everett.webp\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-15009\" alt=\"Close up detail of healthy, shiny African American hair texture being touched by hands with gold ring.\" srcset=\"https:\/\//\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/luxury-natural-hair-care-texture-studio-27-everett.webp 800w, https:\/\//\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/luxury-natural-hair-care-texture-studio-27-everett-200x300.webp 200w, https:\/\//\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/luxury-natural-hair-care-texture-studio-27-everett-683x1024.webp 683w, https:\/\//\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/luxury-natural-hair-care-texture-studio-27-everett-768x1152.webp 768w, https:\/\//\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/luxury-natural-hair-care-texture-studio-27-everett-600x900.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f9a40eb e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"f9a40eb\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-695f456 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"695f456\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">THE EXPERIENCE<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8ee5ae3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8ee5ae3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Our mission at 50 Shades  is to make you look and feel your best. We use only the highest quality products on our exclusive clientele, ensuring that your natural hair is protected while you enjoy your choice of extensions. When you visit us, you can rest assured that you are in experienced hands.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bbff4ab e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"bbff4ab\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e1b29dc elementor-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"e1b29dc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/www.fresha.com\/book-now\/ncozkphf\/all-offer?share=true&#038;pId=426718\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">BOOK YOUR SERVICE<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t",
